description:
Entering college, Wes Peppers completely renounced his faith and became atheist. He had many doubts and couldnt find answers. While planning his own suicide, he felt a mysterious pull to study the Bible. Shortly thereafter, while visiting his Seventh-day Adventist uncle, he received some Bible study guides. The coincidence was too much, so he agreed to study the Word of God, but only to prove it false. Despite trying to prove the Bible false, he kept finding more irrefutable proof that the Bible is true. He started losing confidence in evolution and Wes, once atheist, turned Christian.

For more, please visit our website: https://amazingdiscoveries.org
